{"tid":178461,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"★iPhone5/5c、iPad4走到盡頭，蘋果iOS10.3很可能是最後版本","createTime":"2017-03-29T14:24:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T09:57:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"367754e781a99c798a26a7dcfde1fddfbe749084","tid":178461,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:24:45.000Z","msg":"今天早些時候，蘋果發布了iOS 10.3.2第一個開發者測試版。蘋果並沒有為32位的iOS設備提供iTunes恢復鏡像，比如 iPhone 5和第四代iPad。這意味著iOS 10.3.2發布後，可能將停止對32位iOS設備的支持。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最新的iOS 10.3.2測試版只提供64位設備的恢復鏡像。蘋果並沒有為iPhone 5、iPhone 5c和第四代iPad提供恢復鏡像。iPhone 5、iPhone 5c和iPad 4都搭載蘋果A6或A6X芯片，這也是蘋果發布的最後一款32位芯片。<br />\n<br />\n在2013年，蘋果發布了搭載64位SoC的iPhone 5s，這也預示著未來32位硬體和應用的終結。2015年6月，蘋果提醒開發者，App Store將不接受32位應用。<br />\n去年，iOS 10發布後，蘋果提醒用戶32位應用可能會影響系統性能。最近，當用戶升級至iOS 10.3後，蘋果又提醒32位應用可能不支持未來的iOS版本。這些跡象都顯示32位應用的大限之期將至。<br />\n目前，蘋果是否會在iOS 10.3.2發布後停止支持32位設備還不清楚。目前，iOS 10.3.2正在測試之中，未來可能還會有變化。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ithome.com/html/iphone/302041.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2Fhtml%2Fiphone%2F302041.htm&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=6c78290f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ithome.com/html/iphone/302041.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6922de9a79fe6c26f1ab2dbd1a5b2c1468dbbe2a","tid":178461,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:25:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cceb19bdd7e97f96fe53e8936be721cb65f64417","tid":178461,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:25:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔更新喇<br />\n<br />\n倒水...變磚.....